items-center gap-2 font-bold\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 w-2 h-2 bg-[#7C3AED] rounded-full animate-pulse\"></span>legendary moments</p><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 space-y-3\"><div style=\"animation-delay:0s\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex gap-3 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] mt-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform font-bold leading-[1.7]\">→</span><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">6 ventures across industries, 2 acqusitions</p></div><div style=\"animation-delay:0.1s\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex gap-3 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] mt-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform font-bold leading-[1.7]\">→</span><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">scaled to 1M+ users across products</p></div><div style=\"animation-delay:0.2s\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex gap-3 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] mt-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform font-bold leading-[1.7]\">→</span><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">developed data systems for the nba, verizon, etc.</p></div><div style=\"animation-delay:0.30000000000000004s\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex gap-3 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] mt-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform font-bold leading-[1.7]\">→</span><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">head of an ai medical research team as a uc berkeley freshman</p></div><div style=\"animation-delay:0.4s\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex gap-3 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] mt-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform font-bold leading-[1.7]\">→</span><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">lead 50+ full-time employees before getting my drivers license</p></div><div style=\"animation-delay:0.5s\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex gap-3 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] mt-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform font-bold leading-[1.7]\">→</span><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">bought my mom a car @ 15</p></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 mb-16\"><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-500 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 font-bold\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 w-2 h-2 bg-[#7C3AED] rounded-full animate-pulse\"></span>ongoing quests</p><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 space-y-3\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex gap-3 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] mt-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform font-bold leading-[1.7]\">→</span><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 font-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed\"><a class=\"text-[#7C3AED] hover:text-[#6D28D9] font-semibold relative inline-block group/link\" href=\"#\">amma<span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute -bottom-0.5 left-0 w-0 h-0.5 bg-[#7C3AED] group-hover/link:w-full transition-all duration-300\"></span></a> — ai healthtech startup in stealth mode</p></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 mb-16 max-w-2xl\"><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-light\">i spent a lot of time alone as a child (not always by choice).<br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />this allowed me to develop my own unique style of thinking without external influence.<br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />it's shaped everything i've built so far.<br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" /><br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />if all of this doesn't work out, i'm perfectly happy being homeless for the rest of my life. <br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />at least i'll know i tried.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 mb-16 max-w-2xl\"><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-500 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 font-bold\"><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 w-2 h-2 bg-[#7C3AED] rounded-full\"></span>lore</p><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 mb-8 relative ml-12\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-1 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gray-200\"></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 space-y-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">my first hustle was selling my cousin's old math tests in 5th grade.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">my dad taught me to code when i was 9 y.o.<br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" /></p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">started my first startup building websites for restaurants<br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />expanded to a webdev agency managing 4 full-time devs</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">built a new kind of telemedicine platform for ESL patients <br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />sold to an anonymous hospital chain (1st acquisition)</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">started skipping school to work on my side hustles <br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />founded <a href=\"https://www.lemonhat.io/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] hover:underline font-semibold\">lemonhat</a>: delivery system for local farms (scaled to 100K+ users)</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">worked as a founding eng at <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/prosimo-io/posts/?feedView=all\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] hover:underline font-semibold\">prosimo</a> <br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />got acquired by palo alto networks ($10B)</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">booked a couple amateur modeling shoots bc someone called me chopped</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">graduated valedictorian with 63.22% attendance</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">full-sweeped college apps (except stanford)<br class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3\" />started freshman year at berkeley</p></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 relative pl-8\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 absolute left-0 top-[6px] w-2 h-2 bg-[#C4B5FD] rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light text-[15px]\">skipped my cs final for a <a href=\"https://www.ycombinator.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] hover:underline font-semibold\">yc</a> interview</p></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 mb-6\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex justify-between items-center\"><h3 class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-600 font-bold\">MOTIVATION</h3><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:underline\">OPEN</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 mb-6\"><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 flex justify-between items-center\"><h3 class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-600 font-bold\">Final Level</h3><span class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-[#7C3AED] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:underline\">OPEN</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 pt-16 border-t-2 border-gray-300 text-center\"><p class=\"jsx-4ee4f94afe394e3 text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-mono tracking-wider\">© 2023 anish polakala • lifemaxxer</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fixed top-3 left-1/2 z-[210] flex max-w-[min(96vw,680px)] -translate-x-1/2 flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-1 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white/95 px-2 py-2 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-s